0% — Subject zone: Reference person(s) naturally blended, relit with warm orange sunset rim lighting from the right.\n\nStyle: Hyper-realistic photo composite, cinematic color grade, golden hour warm tones (orange, gold), sharp subject(s), volumetric light rays, professional retouching, 8K quality.\n\nIDENTITY PRESERVATION (apply to every person individually):\nUse the reference image(s) as the only identity source. Preserve exact face structure, jawline, cheekbones, eyes, eyelids, eyebrows, nose shape, lips, skin tone, hair color, hair texture, hairline, age appearance, body proportions, and overall identity for each person. Do not change gender of any person.\n\nPreserve the exact style and type of clothing — tactical uniform, armored vest, gloves, and patches — but render all fabric in Royal Navy Maritime NCD camouflage: large irregular organic blotches of deep charcoal grey, slate blue-grey, dark navy, and black over a mid-grey base. Cool-toned, dark, no greens or browns. Gold/yellow embroidered name patches and rank insignia preserved on chest and shoulders. Camouflage applies uniformly across jacket, trousers, vest, and gloves.\n\nSky: Dramatic warm golden-hour sunset, sweeping voluminous clouds in deep amber, burnished gold, soft cream — cinematic, painterly, sun low on horizon."]}],"links":[[40,"434:348",0,344,0,"CONDITIONING"],[41,343,0,344,1,"IMAGE"],[42,344,0,"434:348",0,"CLIP"],[43,344,1,342,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[],"definitions":{"subgraphs":[{"id":"fab27237-7b45-4a17-9511-d61403b56fa5","version":1,"state":{"lastGroupId":0,"lastNodeId":346,"lastLinkId":44,"lastRerouteId":0},"revision":0,"config":{},"name":"New Subgraph","inputNode":{"id":-10,"bounding":[-899.951412694755,574.7058956353438,128,88]},"outputNode":{"id":-20,"bounding":[2596.93359375,574.7058956353438,128,88]},"inputs":[{"id":"44f586c0-8cb8-45c6-ab5b-5242e448a860","name":"conditioning","type":"CONDITIONING","linkIds":[26],"localized_name":"conditioning","pos":[-795.951412694755,598.7058956353